## Third-Party Components

This project incorporates validated psychometric instruments that have their own licensing requirements:

- **CRS-5 (Centrality of Religiosity Scale)**: Huber, S., & Huber, O. W. (2012)
- **Marlowe-Crowne Social Desirability Scale - Short Form C**: Crowne, D. P., & Marlowe, D. (1960)
- **Godspeed Questionnaire (partial)**: Bartneck, C., et al. (2009)

Users should cite the original authors when using these adapted scales.
